{"name":"cra-server","version":"1.0.3","description":"simple http server with proxy for create-react-app projects","main":"lib/server.js","bin":{"cra-server":"bin/cra-server"},"repository":"https://github.com/ewgenius/cra-server","license":"MIT","devDependencies":{"@types/commander":"^2.3.31","@types/dotenv":"^2.0.20","@types/express":"^4.0.35","@types/node":"^7.0.5","@types/request":"^0.0.40","tslint":"^4.4.2","typescript":"^2.1.6"},"dependencies":{"commander":"^2.9.0","dotenv":"^4.0.0","express":"^4.14.1","request":"^2.79.0"},"scripts":{"build":"rm -rf lib && tsc -p ./"},"gitHead":"ce9ec536a3f0b25acdbe14e2540e5836446996c2","homepage":"https://github.com/ewgenius/cra-server#readme","versions":[{"number":"1.0.0","date":"2017-02-22T09:16:38.140Z"},{"number":"1.0.1","date":"2017-02-22T09:19:55.616Z"},{"number":"1.0.2","date":"2017-02-22T09:27:37.321Z"},{"number":"1.0.3","date":"2017-02-22T10:11:17.158Z"}],"readme":"# CRA Server\n\nSimple express static server with opt-in proxy.\n\n## How to\n\n```\nnpm install --save-dev cra-server\n```\n\nadd in yout package.json:\n\n```\n...\n\"scripts\": {\n  ...\n  \"serve\": \"cra-server\"\n  ...\n}\n```\n\nuse env variables\n\n```\nPORT=3000\nSTATIC_DIR=build\nPROXY_PREFIX=/api\nPROXY_URL=http://<api-server>\n```\n\nor as cli tool\n\n```\ncra-server -p 3000 -d ./build\n```\n\n- -p, --port <port> - specify port, by default is 3000\n- -d, --dir <static-directory> - by default is ./build\n- -url, --proxy-url <proxy-url> - specify proxy url', optional\n- -prefix, --proxy-prefix <proxy-prefix> - specify proxy prefix, optional\n","created":"2017-02-22T09:16:38.140Z","modified":"2017-02-22T10:11:17.158Z","lastPublisher":{"name":"ewgenius","email":"ewgeniux@gmail.com"},"owners":[{"name":"ewgenius","email":"ewgeniux@gmail.com"}],"other":{"_attachments":{},"_from":".","_id":"cra-server","_nodeVersion":"7.3.0","_npmOperationalInternal":{"host":"packages-18-east.internal.npmjs.com","tmp":"tmp/cra-server-1.0.3.tgz_1487758276600_0.04796360083